to speak to ikalgo.

137
00:07:41,962 --> 00:07:45,933
However, this actually worked
in ikalgo’s favor.

138
00:07:47,134 --> 00:07:48,936
Ikalgo: Is this it?

139
00:07:48,969 --> 00:07:51,305
Narrator: As long
as the women stayed put,

